  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Ravens are wary ... very wary. Accustomed to doing the worst jobs in the margins of society (gravediggers, scavengers, garbage collectors), they seem reluctant to put the good judgement that all Corbei have to good use, thanks to which they often simply survive, without ever blooming. They do not like to be at the center of attention, they shy away from responsibility and the pressure of the roles in which they are forced to perform, preferring anonymity and mediocrity. Nonetheless, they are opportunistic and able to keep themselves afloat in any situation: you will never hear about a Raven being a queen on stage, and you similarly never hear about them being beggars or poor. As in every aspect of their life, even in personal relationships, </span>Ravens do not become unbalanced, preferring to maintain </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">superficial and convenient ties. Only with those who persevere in treating them with respect and kindness, showing that they do not feel pity for them or with those who hold them in high esteem, will they accept to open up and offer their rare friendship.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Increase in Ability Scores.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Your  <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Intelligence </span>score increases by 2 and your  <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Constitution </span>score increases by 1.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Age.</strong></em> </span>A Corbei reaches maturity around the age of 14 <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and is immediately considered independent. They have an average lifespan of around 60 years.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Speed.</strong></em> </span></span>Your base speed on the ground is 20 feet, and your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">flight speed is 30 feet.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Size. </strong></em></span>A Raven can reach a height of between 3 1/2 feet <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and 4 1/2 feet, and weigh between 65 lbs and 90 lbs.</span> <span class=\"fontstyle2\">Your size is Medium.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Petty.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You have expertise in the Deception skill.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.ZLta2Wjm3OsgNAk0]{Wings}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.DO8bJUsTURvkwDVu]{Pecking}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.9ALHHLuQoSWQRqN4]{Prehensile Legs}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.fWjnyGpnIsnivS8u]{Fast Learning}</span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[world.species-features.prA3mswGSrkS0JOP]{Great Memory}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.PzL6zz0LevatqjuS]{Gourmet}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.PCBN9c9lNEFp05Af]{Opportunist}</span></p>\n<p><em><strong><span class=\"fontstyle3\">Instinct of Familia, Bad Omen (Omnivore): </span></strong></em><span class=\"fontstyle4\">“I can predict </span><span class=\"fontstyle4\">the worst in any situation.”</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle4\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Instinct of Species, Unfriendly:</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">“I bestow my great friendship only after a long, long time.”</span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /></span></p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
